title: Hour 2 - Tampa Bay Brawl
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Tampa Bay Brawl
description:
On this edition of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan and the Danette's are looking for an explanation for the Tampa Bay Brawl on Sunday, as Buccaneers WR Mike Evans is now staring at a one game suspension.
